ZH: 这个团队的表现太差了，总是掉队。
EN: This team is performing poorly and always lagging behind.

ZH: 我们一起出去玩的时候，他总是掉队。
EN: Whenever we go out together, he always falls behind.

ZH: 她在比赛中掉队了，最后只能沮丧地回家。
EN: She fell behind in the race and could only go home disappointed.

ZH: 在学习中掉队的同学需要更多的帮助。
EN: Students who fall behind in their studies need more help.

ZH: 这个项目进展太慢了，已经开始掉队了。
EN: This project is progressing too slowly and is already falling behind.

ZH:他最近工作太忙，总是掉队。ENNHe has been too busy with work lately and always falls behind.

ZH: 我们需要帮助他们，不要让他们掉队。
EN: We need to help them so they don't fall behind.

ZH: 昨天晚上我迷路了，结果掉队了。
EN: I got lost last night and ended up falling behind.

ZH: 他们太快了，让我掉队了！
EN: They were too fast and made me fall behind!

ZH: 他的学习态度很不积极，很容易掉队。
EN: His attitude towards study is not positive, so he easily falls behind.

ZH: 如果你掉队了，记得喊我们。
EN: If you fall behind, remember to call us.

ZH: 训练的时候，他总是第一个掉队。
EN: During training, he is always the first one to fall behind.

ZH: 在这个团队中，任何一个人都不能掉队。
EN: In this team, no one can fall behind.

ZH: 如果你不主动进步，就会掉队。
EN: If you do not actively improve, you will fall behind.

ZH: 他们在比赛中掉队了，最后没能取得胜利。
EN: They fell behind in the competition and did not win in the end.

ZH: 我们应该帮助那些正在掉队的同学。
EN: We should help those students who are falling behind.

ZH: 我不想在所有人中掉队，所以我努力学习。
EN: I don't want to fall behind everyone else, so I study hard.

ZH: 如果你掉队了，你可以向老师寻求帮助。
EN: If you fall behind, you can seek help from the teacher.

ZH: 他在比赛中掉队了，但还是坚持到终点。
EN: He fell behind in the race but still persisted to the finish line.

ZH: 我们要团结一致，不让任何一个队员掉队。
EN: We need to stick together and not let any team member fall behind.
